name: DPC 2023 SA Winter Tour Division I – presented by ESB Liga Esports
description: Welcome to the ESB Liga Esports DPC 2023 SA Winter Tour Division I! We have the best 8 teams of the region, where they will be facing each other to reach the top 2 positions and win the spot to the first Major of the Winter Tour, in addition to accumulating the highest amount of DPC Points and be closer to the International.
